<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一列火车在美罗城城外的轨道上疾驰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车上运载着一些美罗城动物园的动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这将是一次激动人心的动物园巡游。”火车司机说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”乘务员说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们将会看到一些特别的动物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家一定会很喜欢蓝狒狒。”司机说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是所有人的最爱……天啊！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一列火车开过来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们在美罗城动物园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们站在狒狒馆前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到一座小山和许多树，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是没有看到狒狒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蓝狒狒今天离开动物园去巡游了。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经开始想念它了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望它能早点回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>动物园没有它很没意思。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四个朋友参观飞禽馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“动物园里还有很多很棒的动物。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她指着一只颜色亮丽的鹦鹉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很喜欢鹦鹉皮特。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好！”鹦鹉皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咯咯笑。“你好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真棒！”杰克说，“我看到秃鹫了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉叹了一口气。“这些鸟都很棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我最喜欢的动物还是蓝狒狒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克耸耸肩。“几个月以后，他就会回来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔眼睛突然亮了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个好主意！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以让火箭女孩儿把蓝狒狒带回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那真是太好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉的拳头不停地伸向空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那样我们就不用想蓝狒狒了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怀疑火箭女孩儿能不能做到，特勒尔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么做不到？”特勒尔问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她飞得那么快！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是事实。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过火箭女孩儿不是出租车司机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她有更重要的事情要做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔点点头。“是，你说得对。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西离开朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>确信他们都没有看到以后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她按了一下手表上的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长的脸出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去像是受到了惊吓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚刚发生了严重的火车相撞事故！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”罗西说，“在哪儿发生的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就在美罗城城外。”布洛姆市长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“运载动物园动物的火车跟另一列火车相撞了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一列火车上装满了危险的化学物质。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想我们需要你的帮助！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了咽口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长。我马上就到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>